"releaseNotes":"This update improves reminder notifications so they work more reliably from day to day.\n\nWhat’s fixed:\n\nImproved daily reminder scheduling:\nBetter handling when you complete the puzzle before 8:00 AM\nMore reliable next-day reminder behavior, even if you don’t reopen the app later that day\n\nThanks for playing GIST!", "version":"1.5.1", "wrapperType":"software", "currency":"USD", 
"description":"Every day, a new puzzle is waiting. Your job is to guess the one word that captures the essence of a paragraph — revealed one sentence at a time.\n\nEach wrong guess reveals another sentence as a clue. You have 5 attempts. Simple rules, surprisingly tricky.\n\nGIST is a daily word puzzle that takes less than a minute to play — but might stay with you all day.\n\nHow it works:\n* One sentence is shown as your first clue\n* Guess the one word that captures its meaning\n* Wrong or close guesses reveal more sentences\n* Solve it in as few guesses as possible\n* A new puzzle every day\n\nFeatures:\n* Daily puzzles with varying difficulty — Easy, Medium, Hard, and Wildcard\n* Puzzle archive to catch up on missed days\n* Play past puzzles anytime\n* Share your results with friends\n* Personal stats including win rate, streak, and guess distribution\n* No account needed — just open and play\n* Free to play\n\nWhy GIST?\nMost word games test your vocabulary. GIST tests something different — your ability to read between the lines, find the essence of an idea, and express it in a single word. It's part reading comprehension, part lateral thinking, part intuition.\nNew puzzle every day at midnight. Can you get the GIST?", "languageCodesISO2A":["EN"], "averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":5, "fileSizeBytes":"605184", "formattedPrice":"Free", "minimumOsVersion":"16.0", "price":0.00, "userRatingCount":2}, 
